    "Graphical Abstract IntroductionIn this section, we introduce the motivation of this research, the main research questions, and the structure of the paper.",
    "MotivationNatural language processing (NLP) stands as a technology that facilitates computerhuman interaction through the medium of natural languages.",
    "It encompasses the artificial processing of human language, empowering computers to not only read but also comprehend it.",
    "There are many applications in the field of NLP, covering machine translation, speech recognition, grammar analysis, semantics, and pragmatics.",
    "The core of NLP is to segment text corpora for processing, employing tools like ontology dictionaries, word frequency analytics, and contextual semantic scrutiny to isolate the smallest units of meaning.The key to NLP is to enable natural language communication between humans and computers, where computers not only grasp the meaning of textual language but also express intentions and thoughts in a similar manner."
